  0.20000      MyLambda_c+         pi+    pi-  PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay Myanti-Lambda_c(2940)-

#
#Define Sigma_c++ decay
Decay MySigma_c++
  1.0000    MyLambda_c+  pi+                   PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay Myanti-Sigma_c-- 
#

